<article id="info">
    <title>GT <replaceable role="entity">version</replaceable>: Information Services</title>
    <titleabbrev>Information Services</titleabbrev>
    <para>The Monitoring and Discovery System (MDS) is a suite of web services to monitor and
        discover resources and services on Grids. This system allows users to discover what
        resources are considered part of a Virtual Organization (VO) and to monitor those resources.
        MDS services provide query and subscription interfaces to arbitrarily detailed resource data
        and a trigger interface that can be configured to take action when pre-configured trouble
        conditions are met. GT <replaceable role="entity">version</replaceable> includes WS MDS, the WSRF implementation of MDS.</para>

    <para>For more information about the information services concepts behind GT4, see <olink
            targetdoc="infoKey"/>. </para>
